Hello all,

I have received many requests in the last two years for the sou=
rce code Marcin Suchorzewski wrote for our paper introducing the Developmen=
tal Symbolic Encoding (DSE), the cite of which is

Suchorzewski M, Clune J =
(2011) A novel generative encoding for evolving modular, regular and scalab=
le networks. 
Proceedings of the Genetic and Evolutionary Computation Confe=
rence. 1523-1530. 
pdf: http://jeffclune.com/publications/2011-Suchorzewski=
AndClune-DSE-Gecco.pdf

I am happy to announce that the source code is now =
available. You can access it here: http://jeffclune.com/media/dse_0.7.8.tar=
.gz

If you have any questions about it or the paper, please let me know. I=
f you use it, I'd also be interested to hear about any results you have, in=
cluding papers you publish. 

Best regards,
Jeff Clune

Assistant Professor=

Computer Science
University of Wyoming
jeffclune@...
jeffclune.com


--Apple-Mail=_6F1B9B7C-10E8-42CD-AC71-17E055685C22
